00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,000
The free hack that beats
every supplement for energy.

2
00:00:02,000 --> 00:00:06,000
People spend hundreds on supplements, nootropics,
adaptogens. Most of them do nothing.

3
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:16,000
Bright light in the morning anchors your circadian rhythm. It tells your body
when to be alert and when to sleep. No pill does that.

4
00:00:16,000 --> 00:00:22,000
Step outside within the first hour
after waking. 10-15 minutes. No sunglasses.

5
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:28,000
Link in bio — free
energy profile in 30 seconds.

